{"tid":189791,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【無性夫妻】結婚1年被當透明 支那人妻：只傾過10次電話","createTime":"2017-04-06T16:26:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-08T03:45:31.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5b214b5689018056580df014319e2387c69b31b0","tid":189791,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T16:26:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170405/large/1491399873_30e1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170405%2Flarge%2F1491399873_30e1.jpg&h=74087ee4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n為了達成父母希望自己早日出嫁的願望，廣東惠州26歲楊姓女子去年與認識不足一年的男子結婚，然而二人結婚，卻成了一對有名無實的夫妻。如今楊女只希望與「丈夫」離婚，讓二人關係來一個了斷。<br />\n去年1月，來自惠州26歲的楊小姐在婚戀平台上認識31歲的李姓男子，由於父母希望她早日出嫁，去年9月份，楊小姐在李男湖北的老家註冊結婚。<br />\n楊小姐指，當時父母覺得李男老實，對方父親又供他讀大學，相信為人應可靠。當時楊女對李男認識不深，只知道他在一個單位打工，當時母親不斷催逼女兒註冊，雖然自己不想，但最終只好與對方註冊。<br />\n楊小姐表示，當日李男拿出20萬元(人民幣‧下同)，自己則拿出21萬元，作為在惠州一單位的為首期，二人婚後曾在男方位於番禺大石的租住單位同居過一段時間，二人鮮會溝通，自己不僅有如「透明人」，甚至大家分床而睡。一年下來，雙方只打電話10次，二人甚至從未發生性關係。<br />\n難以忍受的楊小姐後來提出離婚，但雙方一直沒達成協議。楊女即使到廣州找李男，對方亦連電話也不接。楊女早前早前到李男工作的單位了解過，但大廈保安卻指很少見過李男。<br />\n楊女坦言，認為丈夫遲早會拋棄他，覺得對方根本為了自己的錢而來，認為對方不應拖拉。日前，楊小姐終於找到李男，但雙方此終未能就離婚一致協議。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170406/56524779\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170406%2F56524779&d=JcMWRxryG4qpJesfomKpWIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=00e88551\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170406%2F56524779&h=c87f4b50\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170406/56524779</a>"},{"pid":"ec7ab6704ca3dc62d615862db2d1ddaa0ea8657a","tid":189791,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T14:17:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10afa1922c7ae0d1089495c8e6d90b404545501b","tid":189791,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T14:24:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9feef7a8dbcf731ac5b2b57aaec1df0d6f80fdb3","tid":189791,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T16:01:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caf3a49d10150dc2e8ec723beece5d05bb87f3ed","tid":189791,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T17:28:52.000Z","msg":"李男湖北的老家註冊結婚<br />\n<br />\n廣東妹嫁北佬，抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eed25b978506780a5ea38d754d3987d3310423d8","tid":189791,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T02:24:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"107a00d50b784e6e2839eeee6ad0ec9dd26d64d3","tid":189791,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T02:33:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>李男湖北的老家註冊結婚<br />\n<br />\n廣東妹嫁北佬，抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n湖北系華中<br />\n河北先系華北"},{"pid":"2329e74044515b7a99fe7efb6a28dfcb3177194a","tid":189791,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T02:37:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>李男湖北的老家註冊結婚<br />\n<br />\n廣東妹嫁北佬，抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n湖北系華中<br />\n河北先系華北</blockquote><br />\n廣東以上都係北佬是常識吧"},{"pid":"32c20c5eebdbfeb8a2dab458c0ffb9e7c3ab5b05","tid":189791,"uid":61675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T02:42:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>李男湖北的老家註冊結婚<br />\n<br />\n廣東妹嫁北佬，抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n湖北系華中<br />\n河北先系華北</blockquote><br />\n系系系。 系你老母咩"},{"pid":"5afaf8c66911610fcdeaa235168fa6dbbae36f31","tid":189791,"ui